				<ul id="carousel-2" class="testimonials carousel-items clearfix " data-columns="1" data-auto="false"><li class="testimonial carousel-item col-sm-12 clearfix"><div class="testimonial-text"><div style="text-align: justify;">My tryst with engineering began in 2010 when I got admitted in SLIET . I take pride in saying that the foundation laid by SLIET has taken its alumni to influential posts. At SLIET I had my share of enjoyment and excitement whether it be academics, sports or cultural activities. I made lifetime friends. SLIET has always remained unflinching in its commitment to provide transformational education.</div></div><div class="testimonial-cite"><img src="https://www.slietalumni.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/parminder-sekhon-150x150-70x70.jpg" width="70" height="70" alt="MS. PARMINDER KAUR SEKHON" /><div class="cite-text has-cite-image"><span class="cite-name">MS. PARMINDER KAUR SEKHON</span><span class="cite-subtext">Officer - HPCL</span></div></div></li><li class="testimonial carousel-item col-sm-12 clearfix"><div class="testimonial-text"><div style="text-align: justify;">SLIET is a great place to learn and to grow, both as a student and as an individual. Staff will do all they can to give you the wings you need to succeed; you just have to fly. My time at SLIET, gave me the experience &amp; the diverse skill set to begin my career in the professional world. I really appreciate SLIET, the enthusiastic professors &amp; the professional connections I've made during my 7 years stint at SLIET (GME/2K5, 2008 passout).</div></div><div class="testimonial-cite"><img src="https://www.slietalumni.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Dharuv-Picture-150x150-70x70.jpg" width="70" height="70" alt="MR. DHARUV MAHAJAN " /><div class="cite-text has-cite-image"><span class="cite-name">MR. DHARUV MAHAJAN </span><span class="cite-subtext">Volume Planning - Ford Motor Pvt Ltd.</span></div></div></li><li class="testimonial carousel-item col-sm-12 clearfix"><div class="testimonial-text"><div style="text-align@: justify;">SLIET for me is not only a educational temple but a place where you stay amid, very clean,open friendly and harmonious environment among many talented mind from all over the nation. Always cherish those beautiful memories we spent during our hostel and college life.</div></div><div class="testimonial-cite"><img src="https://www.slietalumni.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/sarabjeet-singh-150x150-70x70.jpg" width="70" height="70" alt="MR. SARABJEET SINGH DHANJAL" /><div class="cite-text has-cite-image"><span class="cite-name">MR. SARABJEET SINGH DHANJAL</span><span class="cite-subtext">Manager Programming  ONGC DELHI</span></div></div></li></ul>
